===May I know what...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Sunday:''' May I know what the routines are like on the Express?
:{Choice} Eat
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Three meals a day
::'''Sunday:''' Hmm, the Express crew appears to share similar habits with the Penaconians
:{Choice} Sleep
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Sleep, and one must stay up late before sleep
::'''Sunday:''' Based on my recent observation, it seems like you're the only one with that habit
::'''Sunday:''' Nevertheless, I understand
:{Choice} Massage Pom-Pom
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Offer massage services to the Conductor, of course
::'''Sunday:''' The role of the conductor is indeed challenging and comparable to that of a Family head
:'''Sunday:''' As a passenger, I'd love to help out in some of the daily work
:'''Sunday:''' I'm not sure what I can help with, so I'm here to seek for your advice
:{Choice} Help me sleep
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Play me some bedtime songs to help with my insomnia
::'''Sunday:''' If you don't mind, I can play serenades or lullabies
::'''Sunday:''' Of course, I recommend everyone to listen to Robin's album
:{Choice} Be a good listener
::'''(Trailblazer):''' There are interesting things that happen on a daily basis during trailblazing. You can listen to my rambling
::'''Sunday:''' I used to be a Bronze Melodia. I can probably handle that
:{Choice} Just massage Pom-Pom
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Just offer massage services to our conductor
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Make the Conductor happy, and everyone will be happy
:'''Sunday:''' What a coincidence. I just saw the Conductor
:'''Sunday:''' I'll start with this small task then. I'll massage Pom-Pom for a while
:'''Sunday:''' Thank you for your advice and suggestion
}}
