==={{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} (Trailblazer), I apologize for interrupting===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Sunday:''' {{MC|f=Miss|m=Mr.}} (Trailblazer), I apologize for interrupting
:'''Sunday:''' I brought several desserts and beverages from my hometown, but I'm not sure if they are to your liking
:'''Sunday:''' There are some popular special local products, and others that I personally recommend
:{Choice} I can't believe this...
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I didn't expect you to like these foods!
:'''Sunday:''' I actually haven't been eating as much of them after I become the Family head
:'''Sunday:''' But the other day, I noticed Himeko brewing coffee, which reminded me that Penacony has a drinksmith who infuses SoulGlad into coffee and pairs it with mini dessert pieces tailored to the flavor. That sparked an idea for me
:'''Sunday:''' I can brew a cup of such coffee for Himeko. She'll love it
:{Choice} She's a super-connoisseur
::'''(Trailblazer):''' She's a super-connoisseur
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I thank you on her behalf
:{Choice} Look forward to the competition
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I eagerly await the day when you two compete against each other
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I shall ready a bench and popcorn
:'''Sunday:''' I heard Miss March 7th is a serious dessert lover
:'''Sunday:''' I know of a pudding tart made with ingredients imported from the Xianzhou, and its flavor is said to be remarkably similar to that of the Immortal's Delight
:{Choice} Take less carbs!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Azure Dragon, White Tiger, less carbs!
:'''Sunday:''' A dietitian once recommended that I soak medicinal plants in SoulGlad for three days and nights before drinking it to refresh my mind
:'''Sunday:''' I tried it. It tasted like cooling herbal tea
:'''Sunday:''' Mr. Yang and Dan Heng have been busy with the Express. Perhaps this will be helpful for them
:{Choice} You're too kind
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You're too kind
:{Choice} I can't wait to eat them
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I can't wait to eat them
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I'll finish all these delicacies
:'''Sunday:''' That's great
:'''Sunday:''' Thank you
}}
